HEADWORD: Deemster
<hw>Deem"ster</hw> <pr>(d⟦emac⟧m"st⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Deem</ets> + <ets>-ster</ets>; i. e., doomster. Cf.
<er>Dempster</er>.]</ety> <def>A judge in the Isle of Man who decides
controversies without process.</def> <rj><au>Cowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
